  "detailed_description": "Floor44 is a hardcore luckiness detector kinda game with randomly generated maps, the goal is to make it to the top floor. You can rely on your skills to reach floor30, but you'll need more than that to make it to the Floor44. Make good use of your abilities and collaborate with your team members in order to make it to the higher floor.<br><br>The map will be randomly generated every time so that even I don't know where exactly to go, you can easily get to the top if you were lucky enough to find those super rare items all the time, or you could be very unlucky to have so many wonderers spawned around and make your way hard as hell.<br>Sadly, you can't pause because it is not just a game. Enjoy :)<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Random System</strong>: The map is randomly generated, a lot of events will happen randomly as well, tread carefully.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980770/extras/cc8d7d29bfab173f5b79b7965579a82b.poster.avif?t=1755338298\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980770/extras/cc8d7d29bfab173f5b79b7965579a82b.webm?t=1755338298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980770/extras/cc8d7d29bfab173f5b79b7965579a82b.mp4?t=1755338298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Search any containers, you can find food and drink, rare items and weapons<br><br></li><li><strong>Ability System</strong>: You have to unlock different abilities to survive longer, earn score in game<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980770/extras/25d64c17c80dc5e6dae2365343e5fbf0.poster.avif?t=1755338298\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980770/extras/25d64c17c80dc5e6dae2365343e5fbf0.webm?t=1755338298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980770/extras/25d64c17c80dc5e6dae2365343e5fbf0.mp4?t=1755338298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use your abilities, first you have to unlock them<br><br></li><li><strong>Score System</strong>: Every action in-game could earn your more score, try to reach higher floor and put down more weirdos<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980770/extras/306821c1fa761d23a799ac0003df23bc.poster.avif?t=1755338298\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980770/extras/306821c1fa761d23a799ac0003df23bc.webm?t=1755338298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980770/extras/306821c1fa761d23a799ac0003df23bc.mp4?t=1755338298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Make use of yourself when you are a ghost, disarm traps by held items for your friends<br><br></li><li><strong>Combat System</strong>: Unlike other horror games, you can beat those enemies in game, but you'll have to unlock the ability first.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980770/extras/48efa5b5eadf8b2b4f87dc578a7bf9d3.poster.avif?t=1755338298\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980770/extras/48efa5b5eadf8b2b4f87dc578a7bf9d3.webm?t=1755338298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980770/extras/48efa5b5eadf8b2b4f87dc578a7bf9d3.mp4?t=1755338298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Learn to distinguish real/fake enemies, save your weapon's durability, watch their move closely<br><br><strong>There are much more hidden mechanics waiting for you to discover, I doubt you can make it to the final floor</strong></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Floor44 is a hardcore luckiness detector kinda game with randomly generated maps, the goal is to make it to the top floor. You can rely on your skills to reach floor30, but you'll need more than that to make it to the Floor44. Make good use of your abilities and collaborate with your team members in order to make it to the higher floor.<br><br>The map will be randomly generated every time so that even I don't know where exactly to go, you can easily get to the top if you were lucky enough to find those super rare items all the time, or you could be very unlucky to have so many wonderers spawned around and make your way hard as hell.<br>Sadly, you can't pause because it is not just a game. Enjoy :)<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Random System</strong>: The map is randomly generated, a lot of events will happen randomly as well, tread carefully.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980770/extras/cc8d7d29bfab173f5b79b7965579a82b.poster.avif?t=1755338298\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980770/extras/cc8d7d29bfab173f5b79b7965579a82b.webm?t=1755338298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980770/extras/cc8d7d29bfab173f5b79b7965579a82b.mp4?t=1755338298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Search any containers, you can find food and drink, rare items and weapons<br><br></li><li><strong>Ability System</strong>: You have to unlock different abilities to survive longer, earn score in game<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980770/extras/25d64c17c80dc5e6dae2365343e5fbf0.poster.avif?t=1755338298\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980770/extras/25d64c17c80dc5e6dae2365343e5fbf0.webm?t=1755338298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980770/extras/25d64c17c80dc5e6dae2365343e5fbf0.mp4?t=1755338298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use your abilities, first you have to unlock them<br><br></li><li><strong>Score System</strong>: Every action in-game could earn your more score, try to reach higher floor and put down more weirdos<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980770/extras/306821c1fa761d23a799ac0003df23bc.poster.avif?t=1755338298\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980770/extras/306821c1fa761d23a799ac0003df23bc.webm?t=1755338298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980770/extras/306821c1fa761d23a799ac0003df23bc.mp4?t=1755338298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Make use of yourself when you are a ghost, disarm traps by held items for your friends<br><br></li><li><strong>Combat System</strong>: Unlike other horror games, you can beat those enemies in game, but you'll have to unlock the ability first.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980770/extras/48efa5b5eadf8b2b4f87dc578a7bf9d3.poster.avif?t=1755338298\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980770/extras/48efa5b5eadf8b2b4f87dc578a7bf9d3.webm?t=1755338298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980770/extras/48efa5b5eadf8b2b4f87dc578a7bf9d3.mp4?t=1755338298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Learn to distinguish real/fake enemies, save your weapon's durability, watch their move closely<br><br><strong>There are much more hidden mechanics waiting for you to discover, I doubt you can make it to the final floor</strong></li></ul>",
